    Fetch and parse INMET alerts RSS feed

    parse_feed.Rd

    Fetch and parse INMET alerts RSS feed

    Usage

    parse_feed(progress = TRUE)

    Arguments

    progress

    logical. Show progress bar.

    Value

    a tibble with alerts data

    Examples

    parse_feed()
